  <title translate="true">Ramp Motion-Law</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword translate="true">Asymmetric Motion-Law</keyword>
    <keyword translate="true">Cam Law: Ramp</keyword>
    <keyword translate="true">Motion-Law:<keyword translate="true">Ramp</keyword></keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">Ramp Motion-Law</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_"><text styleclass="Heading3_atocs_" translate="true">Ramp Cam-Law, Motion-Law</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="5" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Interface2" translate="true">Ramp</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true"> has three phases:</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">Phase 1 : Acceleration from zero to maximum velocity</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">Phase 2 : Constant-Velocity</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">Phase 3 : Deceleration from maximum velocity to zero velocity.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="VariableName"><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">You CAN specify the:</text></para>
          <list id="0" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">Start-Position</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true"> (</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">usually </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">flows</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> from the </text><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">End-Position</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> of the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Previous-Segment" styleclass="Element" translate="true">Previous-Segment</link><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true"> )</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Parameter"><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">End-Position</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="VariableName"><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">You </text><text styleclass="VariableName" style="color:#ff0000;" translate="true">CANNOT</text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true"> specify the:</text></para>
          <list id="1" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">Start-Velocity, End-Velocity</text></li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">Start-Acceleration, End-Acceleration</text></li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">Start-Jerk, End-Jerk</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Parameter-Header"><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">Segment-Parameters</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">Start-Fraction</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> x </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">100 %</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> = % of the segment from zero to maximum velocity.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">End-Fraction</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">x 100 %</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> = </text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">% of the segment from maximum to zero velocity.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_"><image src="MT-SE-Ramp-SegmentParameters.png" scale="-99.90%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"><caption translate="true"><![CDATA[Segment Parameters Ramp Motion-Law]]></caption></image></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.00; background-color:transparent; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; border:none; tabstops:none;"><image src="MT-CamLaw-Ramp.ipp" scale="-99.90%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"><caption translate="true"><![CDATA[1 x Ramp Segment, Symmetrical]]></caption></image></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="VariableName"><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Applications</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">Motion with a long move in which the Maximum-Velocity of a different motion-law would be too high.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true">Use a </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Ramp</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true"> to reduce the peak velocity of a segment.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">With a Cam, you can reduce the maximum pressure-angle. However, the maximum-acceleration will increase.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="vertical-align:top; height:21px;">
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><image src="MT-CamLaw-Ramp-Example.ipp" scale="-99.90%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"><caption translate="true"><![CDATA[E.g.: RAMP Segment: Start-Fraction = 0.7, End-Fraction = 0.3
(Constant-Velocity Fraction = 0)]]></caption></image></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="vertical-align:top; height:21px;">
          <para styleclass="Interface2"><text styleclass="Interface2" translate="true">EXAMPLE : </text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true">Use the </text><text styleclass="Interface2" translate="true">Ramp</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true"> Motion-Law to design an </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Asymmetrical motion</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">In the example, image above:</text></para>
          <list id="2" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">Start-Fraction</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Body Text" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">≠</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">End-Fraction</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">&#32;</text></li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">Start-Fraction</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true"> is 0.7</text></li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">End-Fraction</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true"> is 0.3</text></li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">Start-Fraction</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true"> + </text><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">End-Fraction</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true"> = 1, therefore, Constant-Velocity Fraction = 0</text></li>
          </list>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
